    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a B2B lead qualification specialist.\n\nAnalyze this lead and determine:\n\n1. lead_score\n- Hot\n- Warm\n- Cold\n\n2. reason\n\nLead Information\n\nName:\n{{ $json.Name }}\n\nCompany:\n{{ $json.Company }}\n\nBudget:\n{{ $json.Budget }}\n\nMessage:\n{{ $json.Message }}\n\n\nAnalyze the lead and provide:\n- lead_score (Hot, Warm, or Cold)\n- reason\n\nFollow the required output format.\n\nLead Score Rules:\n\nHot:\n- Budget above $20,000\n- Clear business need\n\nWarm:\n- Budget $5,000–$20,000\n- Interest shown but not urgent\n\nCold:\n- No budget\n- Just browsing\n\nIMPORTANT:\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON.\n\nExample:\n\n{\n  \"lead_score\": \"Hot\",\n  \"reason\": \"Large budget and clear business need\"\n}\n\nDo not add explanations.\nDo not add markdown.\nDo not use lead_score: Hot format.\nReturn JSON only.\n",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {}
      },
